{"tid":1759762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣】香港議會制度","createTime":"2019-11-27T23:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T00:56:38.000Z","uid":81167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dde4b02606adec43e6a3bc380a77b2a2cc71d800","tid":1759762,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T23:48:58.000Z","msg":"我突然間有個諗法，就係外國嘅人未必清楚香港嘅議會制度，有機會以為區議會民主派大勝就認為香港已經有民主。<br />\n<br />\n文宣同國際戰線可以考慮下詳細宣傳一下其實香港嘅議會制度係點，特首係點樣產生，等全世界知道香港其實未贏，仲有一條好長嘅路要走。咁樣人地先會明白點解區議會過後仍然會有唔同嘅抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係，人地可能會唔明點解，變左覺得好似香港人搞亂檔咁。香港抗爭者嘅形象係好重要。我地係智取，唔可以浪費前線同埋咁多位手足一直嘅努力同埋所建立嘅形象。我地要明白自己嘅長短處，放大香港人嘅優點，同時縮小缺點。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油"},{"pid":"5e15f8e5a500b3d6adb97b75ddbdb2a697aec9f4","tid":1759762,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T23:49:36.000Z","msg":"希望大家會睇曬"},{"pid":"30f424ffe6001ca8ee10a5698a1687356b1c4ac5","tid":1759762,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T23:50:26.000Z","msg":"有用po，麻煩睇下"},{"pid":"9df5b3ce255da1f8ab6991d7a1fb893038380e73","tid":1759762,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T23:53:32.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"74cc684beb2afaa5637e42842dd9188fdc531503","tid":1759762,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T23:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15d2fdf2dbdd6487bd7ec0762f93641250bad9a","tid":1759762,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T23:55:10.000Z","msg":"我打左好耐ga，睇下啦～"},{"pid":"83648f2c6235c198e4da295653b9611da6afd989","tid":1759762,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T23:57:31.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"61dccba39e7767c037c97284e3fd9613059812a9","tid":1759762,"uid":81167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0